    {
      "id": "edge-class-contract-overview",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Edge Class Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": -80,
        "y": -140
      },
      "width": 560,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Edge Class Contract\n\nPlain edges remain the baseline relationship object. A graph can always draw a simple edge without declaring a class.\n\nEdge classes are an optional semantic upgrade. When an edge needs reusable meaning, legend exposure, or shared render defaults, the base edge may carry an optional `edgeClassKey` that points at an addressable edge-class artifact.\n\nCurrent bridge doctrine:\n\n- the edge remains the thing being authored\n- the class artifact remains the semantic authority when linked\n- the legend is an exposure surface, not the authority\n- bridge flows should copy enough class metadata into the host legend for humans and renderers, but they should not create a second semantic home\n\nThis graph defines the minimal contract for that model.",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
            },
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "node",
              "payload": "node.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
              "version": ">=0.1.0"
            }
          ],
          "nodeView": {
