    {
      "id": "edge-class-contract-task-fields",
      "type": "task",
      "label": "Define the minimal field set",
      "position": {
        "x": -40,
        "y": 220
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 220,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "body": "Default minimal field set: `key`, `label`, `meaning`, `defaultEdgeType`, `usageGuidance`, `sourceKinds`, `targetKinds`, `legendRole`, `semanticAuthority`, and a small `renderDefaults` block. `defaultStyle` as a giant catch-all is too vague; prefer explicit render defaults.",
