    {
      "id": "edge-class-contract-defaults",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Default Contract",
      "position": {
        "x": 1240,
        "y": 520
      },
      "width": 620,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Default Contract\n\nBase edge rule:\n\n- a plain edge remains fully valid without a class\n- `data.edgeClassKey` is optional, not required\n- adding an edge class upgrades the edge with reusable semantics and defaults\n\nAn edge class should default to:\n\n- `key`\n- `label`\n- `meaning`\n- `defaultEdgeType`\n- `usageGuidance`\n- `sourceKinds`\n- `targetKinds`\n- `legendRole`\n- `semanticAuthority`\n- small `renderDefaults` such as:\n  - `stroke`\n  - `width`\n  - `dash`\n  - `labelTone`\n  - `routingHint`\n\nBridge doctrine:\n- the class artifact remains the semantic authority\n- a host legend may mirror class metadata for local reading and render resolution\n- mirrored legend metadata is not a second semantic home\n\nDefaults:\n- the class owns semantic meaning\n- the class may carry light render defaults\n- the legend should expose, not invent, class meaning\n- edge instances may override rendering\n- instance values win when both are present\n- plain `reference` edges remain valid when no stronger semantic contract is needed",
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
          "identity": {
            "graphId": "markdown_class",
            "name": "markdown Node Class",
            "version": "0.1.0",
            "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
            "createdAt": "2026-02-24T20:05:15Z",
            "updatedAt": "2026-03-24T01:20:00.000Z"
          },
          "intent": "graph",
          "meaning": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "description": "Canonical markdown content node.",
          "defaults": {},
          "nodeDef": {
            "key": "markdown",
            "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
            "source": "local",
            "version": ">=0.1.0"
          },
          "views": [
            {
              "key": "markdown",
              "intent": "editor",
              "payload": "editor.web",
              "ref": "/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
              "source": "local",
